name: Star Wars imperial officer uniform
description:
Somebody commented that this is the last thing to do to close all the iconic suits from SW, so i did.

Trigger is imperialofficer uniform.

Updated V2:

-is much more consistent and better looking.

-You can now use "white imperialofficer uniform" to get ISB version from Andor.

-Best results with 0,7 or 0,8 weight.

-It no longer tries to add buttons and skirts.

Add "hat" to the prompt to get the headwear.

As there is no one color of the uniform you should add the desired color to prompt if you want to have a specific one.
